EmailTemplate.subject: Live Different Build: Forms Needed
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Hi {!Contact.FirstName},
I hope you are having a great weekend so far. Your trip is coming up very soon! We are trying to get all your forms in order and I was hoping you could help me out.
Could you please sign the attached forms and send them back to me?
You can scan them or take a picture of the forms. You can then email them back to me or upload them to your volunteer page. It's up to you!
Please let me know if you have any questions. Talk soon!
